  "prompt": "Which is the best modular kitchen in india?",
  "response": "Choosing the \"best\" modular kitchen in India can be subjective and depend on individual preferences, budget, and specific needs. However, some reputable brands are widely recognized for their quality, design, and customer satisfaction:\n\n1. **Sleek by Asian Paints**: Known for contemporary designs and a wide range of customization options, Sleek provides high-quality finishes and reliable after-sales service.\n\n2. **Godrej Interio**: Offers a variety of design choices catering to different tastes and budgets, with a strong focus on durability and functionality.\n\n3. **Livspace**: This brand provides end-to-end solutions from design to installation, featuring modern aesthetics and highly customizable options.\n\n4. **Hettich**: Renowned for its innovative fittings and hardware, Hettich modular kitchens are highly functional and stylish.\n\n5. **Ultrafresh**: Focuses on providing durable modular kitchen solutions with efficient space utilization and modern designs.\n\n6. **IFB Modular Kitchens**: Known for their stylish and ergonomic designs, blending technology and aesthetics seamlessly.\n\n7. **Kitchens by Design**: Offers premium kitchen designs with a focus on luxury and high-quality craftsmanship.\n\n8. **Arttd\u2019inox**: Specializes in stainless steel modular kitchens, known for their durability, hygiene, and contemporary designs.\n\nTo determine the best option for you, consider visiting showrooms, seeking customer reviews, consulting design experts, and comparing features and prices. Additionally, professional advice tailored to your specific requirements can help make an informed decision.",
